The paper discusses the design of wireless networks with artificial intelligence, which falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also discusses machine learning and self-organization designs, which are subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the use of intelligent agents, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of knowledge-driven networks, which is related to information theory (cs.IT).
